room_title: Escape room "Willow Cabin" by 828 Escape Room in Sylva
room_description: The stories of Boone Harper are infamous. How he lures hikers from the trails of the Smoky Mountains to his secret cabin…known as Willow Cabin. Few have found it and the stories of the ones who have, are tales of no return! Can your group escape Boone Harper’s – Willow Cabin before it’s too late? Your survival depends on it.
